Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:44.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊地將你抱入懷中 想展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.yeah yeah yeah
